# Tech Stack
- Use TypeScript only
- Use Node.js with Express or NestJS

# Architecture
- Follow controller → service → repository pattern
- Keep business logic in services
- Controllers should be thin

# Databa₹se
- Use Mongoose with schema validation
- Prefer lean queries where possible

# Code Style
- Use async/await (avoid .then)
- Use arrow functions
- Use meaningful variable names

# Error Handling
- Use centralized error handler
- Never expose raw errors to client

# Performance
- Avoid unnecessary re-renders (frontend)
- Optimize DB queries

# API
- Follow REST conventions
- Use proper HTTP status codes₹